ElementMapper<IN,GETTER_OUT,SETTER_IN,OUT> - Class in es.utils.mapper.impl.element
This class contains the informations and the logic needed the execute the mapping of an single element: a Getter: a function tha take a IN type object a Transformer: a function that maps the result of the getter into the correct type for the setter a Setter: a operation that assign the result of the transformer to the destination object
